i added level three and uploaded it on rapidshare because my friend wanted to play it ^^, who ever wants to test it visit http://rapidshare.com/files/234743466/surf_landscapes_beta_lvl1-3.bsp.html . the problem is that you can only download it 10 times because i dont have a rapidshare account ... :P
but level 3 isnt even in beta status so u can wait for my next fpsb release

To be able to play this map on your own server u have to add "-tickrate 66" to your launch options of counterstrike source. ingame type sv_airaccelerate 150 and it should work.

this is the beta of level 1 and 2.

have fun testing the map, please send me some feedback too.
